HEADWORD: Avener
<hw>Av"e*ner</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>avenier</ets>, fr. <ets>aveine</ets>, <ets>avaine</ets>,
<ets>avoine</ets>, oats, F. <ets>avoine</ets>, L.
<ets>avena</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Feud. Law)</fld> <def>An officer of the
king's stables whose duty it was to provide oats for the horses.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
